overview:
Rainmaker LLC based in Lake Worth Florida provides quality installation and service to lawn sprinkling systems.

To be effective irrigating plant material and turf in South Florida it is important to have knowledge of best practices for plant material in South Florida. For this reason we have a Certified Master Gardener on staff to provide advice to clients and train our technicians how South Florida plant material and turf should be cared for.

Our professional service technicians can visit your site and solve any sprinkler problem.

Call us for service 561-585-9916 or visit our web site.

We will go through your lawn sprinklers, do an evaluation and recommend any needed repairs.

Free estimates.

We offer monthly service agreements.

Monthly visits are made to your site and all sprinkling systems are gone through by our professional technicians to locate and repair any issue discovered during inspection.

We install drip irrigation for use with low maintenance green spaces.
